#: admin/com_vikbooking:VBNEWIVATAXCAPHELP
msgid "A tax cap places an upper bound on the amount of government tax a company might be required to pay. In this case the tax is said to be capped. This function is only required for some countries, where there is a limit (maximum amount) of taxes that should be paid. Please ignore this setting if nothing similar applied to your country of residence."
